    <briefdescription>
<para>SHA-256 cryptographic hash — pure C99, zero dependencies. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Follows the same streaming pattern as <ref refid="syn__crc_8h" kindref="compound">syn_crc.h</ref>: init → update (repeated) → final</para>
<para>The context struct is caller-owned (~112 bytes on 32-bit targets). No heap allocation, no floating point, no external libraries.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Usage</title><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>One-shot:</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">uint8_t<sp/>hash[32];</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="syn__sha256_8h_1a26ebdfb51601b7ce315872c4131ca23b" kindref="member">syn_sha256</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;abc&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/>3,<sp/>hash);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Streaming:</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structSYN__SHA256" kindref="compound">SYN_SHA256</ref><sp/>ctx;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="syn__sha256_8c_1ac64650c12d9cdd0e278e09086ddae7b6" kindref="member">syn_sha256_init</ref>(&amp;ctx);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="syn__sha256_8c_1ae5d5f928109f942592d41ca545158f02" kindref="member">syn_sha256_update</ref>(&amp;ctx,<sp/>chunk1,<sp/>len1);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="syn__sha256_8c_1ae5d5f928109f942592d41ca545158f02" kindref="member">syn_sha256_update</ref>(&amp;ctx,<sp/>chunk2,<sp/>len2);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="syn__sha256_8c_1a03f691b9ec17b2fcbd6224252b7b1ff6" kindref="member">syn_sha256_final</ref>(&amp;ctx,<sp/>hash);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
